These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, dressmaker, security-guard, videographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, martial-arts, horror, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: snake, hamster, mouse, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, surfing, handball, skateboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, tram, helicopter, roller
 1. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 4. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is the person watching time-travel movies##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 9. the security-guard is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
10. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
11. the writer is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the owner of the mouse is between the person watching horror movies and the owner of the hamster##2
13. the security-guard is the person driving the roller##1
14. the person driving the helicopter is the dressmaker##1
15. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Job           | writer | security-guard | videographer  | dressmaker    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts     | time-travel   | horror  | musical  |
| Pet           | hamster        | mouse    | lizard        | snake |
| Sport         | skateboarding    | surfing      | water-polo   | handball    |
| Transport     | scooter  | roller     | tram | helicopter |

