.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, tea, 7up
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, collecting, filmmaking, rock-climbing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, musical, time-travel, romance
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, rock, ambient, punk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, handball, tennis, basketball
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
 4. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 5. the person watching romance movies is the person who's sport is handball##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 9. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
10. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
12. the fan of classical is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
13. the fan of rock is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea        | 7up       | lemonade    | hot-chocolate       |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | collecting      | rock-climbing | woodworking |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | time-travel | musical  | documentary   |
| Music-Genre   | rock   | punk         | classical   | ambient      |
| Sport         | handball      | skiing     | tennis    | basketball      |

