.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, apple, apricot, cucumber
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, videographer, writer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, hip-hop, salsa, trance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, weightlifting, sailing, skiing
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, jet-ski, snowmobile, trike
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the fan of hip-hop##1
 2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 3. the person driving the trike is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the coach##3
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person eating apple##3
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
 7. the writer is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
10. the person eating apricot is the fan of salsa##1
11. the fan of trance is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
12. the fan of trance is on the right of the videographer##1
13. the person who's sport is sailing is the person eating cucumber##1
14. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | apricot | apple | pumpkin     | cucumber |
| Job           | videographer  | writer   | coach | dressmaker  |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | trance      | hip-hop     | classical   |
| Sport         | skiing | tennis  | weightlifting   | sailing    |
| Transport     | snowmobile | jet-ski    | trike     | scooter |

