.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, skydiving, camping, photography
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, videographer, lawyer, fisherman
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, country, folk
4 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, hamster, ferret
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, boat, skateboard, taxi
 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 2. the fan of country is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
 4. the fan of folk is between the person driving the bus and the person driving the skateboard##2
 5. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 8. the owner of the goldfish is the person driving the boat##1
 9. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
10. the videographer is on the left of the pilot##1
11. the fisherman is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the fisherman##1
13. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
14. the videographer is on the left or right of the pilot##3
15. the lawyer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |        4        |
| Hobby         | photography | skydiving    | magic-tricks | camping       |
| Job           | videographer | pilot  | fisherman   | lawyer |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | house     | folk      | country            |
| Pet           | goat       | hamster      | goldfish    | ferret           |
| Transport     | taxi      | skateboard | boat   | bus         |

