.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, pumpkin, spinach, grapes
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, project-manager, engineer, software-developer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, zombie, time-travel, adventure
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, dog, hedgehog, fish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, ice-hockey, basketball, skiing
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person eating pumpkin##2
 2. the engineer is in an even position##4
 3. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the engineer##1
 4. the software-developer is in an even position##4
 5. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 7. the person eating spinach is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
 9. the dressmaker is the person eating grapes##1
10. the person eating pumpkin is the person watching adventure movies##1
11. the dressmaker is the person watching comedy movies##1
12. the owner of the hedgehog is the person watching zombie movies##1
13. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
14. the person eating pumpkin is the software-developer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |       4        |
| Food          | grapes   | papaya        | spinach      | pumpkin      |
| Job           | dressmaker | engineer         | project-manager   | software-developer |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy       | time-travel          | zombie | adventure        |
| Pet           | guinea-pig         | dog    | hedgehog    | fish         |
| Sport         | ice-hockey     | basketball | skiing  | rugby        |

