There 4 different types of food: lemon, broccoli, tomato, cucumber
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, puzzles, collecting, singing
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, designer, social-worker, doctor
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, adventure, disaster, satire
 1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the person eating cucumber is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 4. the doctor is in an odd position##4
 5. the person watching crime movies is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 6. the dancer is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 7. the person watching satire movies is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 8. the designer is the person drinking water##1
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating tomato is the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person watching satire movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
13. the person eating broccoli is in an odd position##4
14. the designer is between the person eating tomato and the person who's hobby is singing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
