.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-7::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, asparagus, avocado, potato
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, rock-climbing, writing, singing
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, dancer, analyst, accountant
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, trance, jazz, gospel
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, australian, canadian, malaysian
 1. the dancer is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 2. the australian is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
 4. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
 5. the colombian is on the left or right of the accountant##3
 6. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is the malaysian##1
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the fan of trance and the colombian##2
 9. the analyst is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating strawberry is in an even position##4
11. the colombian is on the right of the canadian##1
12. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the writer##3
13. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
14. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the malaysian##1
15. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |       4        |
| Food          | potato     | strawberry  | avocado     | asparagus         |
| Hobby         | reading  | rock-climbing       | writing | singing    |
| Job           | writer | accountant | dancer  | analyst |
