.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta, milk, cola
There 4 different types of food: pepper, cabbage, watermelon, corn
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, filmmaking, camping, dancing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, superhero, animation, documentary
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, skateboarding, snowboarding, lacrosse
 1. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person watching superhero movies##1
 4. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person drinking milk##1
 5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's hobby is camping##2
 7. the person drinking cola is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching documentary movies##2
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 9. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
10. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
11. the person eating cabbage is the person who's hobby is camping##1
12. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | milk    | cola      | fanta      | iced-tea |
| Food          | pepper | watermelon | corn       | cabbage |
| Hobby         | writing   | dancing   | filmmaking | camping  |
