 2. the person eating garlic is the person drinking milk##1
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
 7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
10. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
11. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
12. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
13. the person watching family movies is the person eating mango##1
14. the person eating mango is the person drinking 7up##1
15. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3

