.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, filmmaking, sudoku, rock-climbing
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, dressmaker, teacher, designer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, folk, ambient, techno
4 different pets are kept: bird, rat, dog, turtle
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, train, scooter, helicopter
 1. the person driving the car is the owner of the bird##1
 2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 3. the designer is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 6. the teacher is on the left of the dressmaker##1
 7. the owner of the rat is the designer##1
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the owner of the bird##1
 9. the person driving the scooter is between the fan of ambient and the dressmaker##2
10. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the car is on the left of the fan of folk##1
13. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
14. the dressmaker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | board-games       | filmmaking    | rock-climbing | sudoku     |
| Job           | designer | teacher  | dressmaker  | nurse       |
| Music-Genre   | ambient         | jazz        | techno     | folk |
| Pet           | rat    | dog   | bird       | turtle     |
| Transport     | helicopter          | scooter | car      | train |

