.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water, sprite, tea
There 4 different types of food: corn, pomegranate, grapefruit, raspberry
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, writer, lawyer, accountant
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, sports, family, epic
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, van, subway, scooter
 1. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
 2. the accountant is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the teacher is the person drinking water##1
 4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 5. the person driving the scooter is between the person drinking tea and the writer##2
 6. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
 8. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
 9. the writer is the person eating raspberry##1
10. the person watching sports movies is the person eating grapefruit##1
11. the accountant is on the left of the person drinking water##1
12. the person watching drama movies is between the person driving the subway and the person watching sports movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |     3      |       4       |
| Beverage      | almond-milk          | tea     | water       | sprite |
| Food          | pomegranate    | corn      | grapefruit   | raspberry          |
| Job           | lawyer   | accountant | teacher   | writer   |
| Movie-Genre   | family | drama    | sports     | epic        |
| Transport     | subway         | van    | scooter | snowmobile           |

