.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-18::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, watermelon, broccoli, cauliflower
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, coach, architect, photographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, musical, scientific, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: pony, mouse, ferret, bird
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, trike, skateboard, scooter
 1. the coach is the person watching time-travel movies##1
 2. the photographer is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is the person driving the scooter##1
 4. the owner of the pony is between the owner of the mouse and the person eating strawberry##2
 5. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating strawberry is the person driving the skateboard##1
 8. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the photographer##3
10. the photographer is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
11. the architect is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
12. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
13. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the architect##3
14. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3

.:: Answer ::.
