| Job           | manager | architect | coach  | photographer |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | zombie | time-travel    | scientific          |
| Pet           | bird  | mouse   | pony       | ferret           |
| Transport     | airplane | scooter      | trike | skateboard            |

