.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, coffee, sprite, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, metal, folk, d&b
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, russian, french
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, water-polo, badminton, swimming
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, ship, van, scooter
 1. the person driving the scooter is the person drinking cola##1
 2. the person drinking water is on the right of the dutch##1
 3. the fan of d&b is the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the ship is the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
 7. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 8. the french is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
10. the russian is on the left or right of the french##3
11. the person who's sport is swimming is the egyptian##1
12. the fan of disco is on the far left or far right##3
13. the fan of metal is between the person drinking water and the person who's sport is rowing##2
14. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the fan of metal##1
15. the fan of d&b is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |       4       |
| Beverage      | sprite | cola      | coffee    | water           |
| Music-Genre   | d&b   | folk | metal    | disco       |
| Nationality   | french | russian     | dutch | egyptian     |
| Sport         | badminton  | rowing    | water-polo | swimming |
| Transport     | ship     | scooter      | van     | train      |

