.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, 7up, iced-tea, coffee
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, raspberry, zucchini, cabbage
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, cooking, sudoku, reading
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, comedy, martial-arts, musical
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, airplane, snowmobile, subway
 1. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 3. the person driving the airplane is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person eating zucchini is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching comedy movies is in an odd position##4
10. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
11. the person driving the van is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
12. the person eating cabbage is the person drinking coffee##1
13. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | almond-milk        | coffee      | iced-tea | 7up         |
| Food          | zucchini      | cabbage      | pomegranate  | raspberry         |
| Hobby         | reading | board-games      | cooking  | sudoku |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts      | musical | comedy  | crime        |
| Transport     | subway       | van        | snowmobile  | airplane           |

 